subject: Rugby (Game)
lead_paragraph: Argentina defeated France, 34-10, yesterday at Parc des Princes in Paris to claim third place at the Rugby World Cup and record its sixth victory in seven matches against France. The final between England and South Africa is tonight in Paris.
